00:01:22.670 --> 00:01:28.220 align:middle line:10%
life, namely the challenge to
battle against sectarianism.

00:01:28.220 --> 00:01:32.840 align:middle line:84%
>> Yes, he felt sorry, because
he wanted to help people,

00:01:32.840 --> 00:01:37.170 align:middle line:84%
but he wanted, more than this,
