00:02:56.230 --> 00:02:57.680 align:middle line:90%
Old MacDonald--

00:02:57.680 --> 00:03:01.820 align:middle line:84%
>> The South Devon School is one
of 35 Steiner Waldorf Schools

00:03:01.820 --> 00:03:03.230 align:middle line:90%
in Britain.

00:03:03.230 --> 00:03:07.520 align:middle line:84%
The first Waldorf School was
founded by Steiner in 1919

00:03:07.520 --> 00:03:11.780 align:middle line:84%
at the request of Emil Molt,
owner of the Waldorf cigarette

00:03:11.780 --> 00:03:15.830 align:middle line:84%
factory in Stuttgart, who wanted
an education for the children

00:03:15.830 --> 00:03:19.730 align:middle line:84%
of his employees that prepared
them for life in its fullest

00:03:19.730 --> 00:03:21.920 align:middle line:90%
sense.

00:03:21.920 --> 00:03:24.590 align:middle line:84%
And life in its
fullest sense means

00:03:24.590 --> 00:03:28.190 align:middle line:84%
educating hands and
heart, as well as head.

00:03:28.190 --> 00:03:31.790 align:middle line:84%
Until the children go into class
one around the age of seven,

00:03:31.790 --> 00:03:36.140 align:middle line:84%
the emphasis is on play,
imitation, and on rhythm--

00:03:36.140 --> 00:03:39.020 align:middle line:84%
baking on Monday,
painting on Wednesday,

00:03:39.020 --> 00:03:41.810 align:middle line:84%
an expedition on
Thursday, and so on.

00:03:41.810 --> 00:03:44.120 align:middle line:84%
And on stories,
which are told rather

00:03:44.120 --> 00:03:47.715 align:middle line:90%
than read by the teacher.

00:03:47.715 --> 00:03:50.810 align:middle line:84%
And Steiner's picture
of child development

00:03:50.810 --> 00:03:54.050 align:middle line:84%
is not only of children growing
up, and thereby learning

00:03:54.050 --> 00:03:58.100 align:middle line:84%
the ways of the world, but
also of children growing down,

00:03:58.100 --> 00:04:01.460 align:middle line:84%
bringing into life their
own unique biographies--

00:04:01.460 --> 00:04:04.200 align:middle line:84%
as he saw it, from
many lifetimes.

00:04:04.200 --> 00:04:05.690 align:middle line:10%
And this needs time--

00:04:05.690 --> 00:04:08.900 align:middle line:10%
time to build a strong
and firm foundation

00:04:08.900 --> 00:04:12.920 align:middle line:10%
so that each child can not only
then face the world as it is,

00:04:12.920 --> 00:04:18.800 align:middle line:10%
but also develop the strength
of character to maybe change it.

00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:21.980 align:middle line:84%
These nine-year-olds are
not just studying farming,

00:04:21.980 --> 00:04:26.390 align:middle line:84%
but actually doing it as part
of what is called main lesson--

00:04:26.390 --> 00:04:29.390 align:middle line:84%
one particular subject taught
for the first two hours

00:04:29.390 --> 00:04:33.440 align:middle line:84%
every morning over a period
of three or four weeks.

00:04:33.440 --> 00:04:35.870 align:middle line:84%
Around this age,
most children start

00:04:35.870 --> 00:04:37.820 align:middle line:84%
to take a new
interest in the world

00:04:37.820 --> 00:04:41.000 align:middle line:84%
around them whilst
also experiencing

00:04:41.000 --> 00:04:43.940 align:middle line:84%
a certain separation
from that world.

00:04:43.940 --> 00:04:47.180 align:middle line:84%
Now they begin to study
science, and in mathematics,

00:04:47.180 --> 00:04:48.800 align:middle line:90%
